  Users Table
  +-----------------+--------------+-------------------+
  | Field Name      | Data Type    | Constraints       |
  +-----------------+--------------+-------------------+
  | ID              | INT          | Primary key       |
  | Email           | VARCHAR(50)  | Unique            |
  | Password        | VARCHAR(255) |                   |
  | Role            | INT          |                   |
  +-----------------+--------------+-------------------+

  Branches Table
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+
  | Field Name              | Data Type        | Constraints                |
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+
  | ID                      | INT              | Primary key                |
  | ParentBranchID          | INT              | Nullable,                  |
  |                         |                  | Foreign Key (Branches.ID)  |
  | Title                   | VARCHAR(255)     |                            |
  | PrimaryDocument         | VARCHAR(255)     |                            |
  | PrimaryExplanatoryDoc   | VARCHAR(255)     |                            |
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+

  Permissions Table
  +-------------------+------------+---------------------------+
  | Field Name        | Data Type  | Constraints               |
  +-------------------+------------+---------------------------+
  | PermissionID      | INT        | Primary key               |
  | UserID            | INT        | Foreign Key (Users.ID)    |
  | BranchID          | INT        | Foreign Key (Branches.ID) |
  | IsOwner           | BOOLEAN    |                           |
  +-------------------+------------+---------------------------+

    Commits Table
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+
  | Field Name              | Data Type        | Constraints                |
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+
  | Hash                    | VARCHAR(255)     | Primary key                |
  | Branch                  | INT              | Foreign Key (Branches.ID)  |
  | IsPublished             | BOOLEAN          |                            |
  | AcceptationStatus       | INT              |                            |
  +-------------------------+------------------+----------------------------+

    Tokens Table
  +------------------+--------------+-----------------------------+
  | Field Name       | Data Type    | Constraints                 |
  +------------------+--------------+-----------------------------+
  | TokenID          | INT          | PRIMARY KEY                 |
  | UserID           | INT          | FOREIGN KEY (Users.ID)      |
  | TokenValue       | VARCHAR(255) |                             |
  | ExpiryDate       | TIMESTAMP    |                             |
  +------------------+--------------+-----------------------------+

